Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類一直在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與來自神秘遠方的敵人－{\fnArial}Festum{\fnSimHei}戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你死就是我亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此毫無妥協的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了保存一些人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一些人犧牲了
