Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:47.26,pic1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(551,425)\frz-20}歡慶畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舉行了那一年的第二個「畢業」典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…今與諸位學長分別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人深感惆悵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們決不會忘記諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也請學長們一切珍重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勿忘島上渡過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衷心祝願身體健康 工作順利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.22,0:03:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謹表贈別之意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭賀諸位畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有學生會長氣勢的告別辭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 副會長幫我斟酌的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道 你這懶蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要和你分別了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空會回來轉轉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「畢業」成了定局之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得有些不適應 對這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡快融入大人之中反而更輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也早點確定自己的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁還能活在義務教育世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如向喜歡的人告白之類的 什麼都行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心存遺憾是最糟糕的 肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有留下遺憾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了 僚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,義務教育都沒完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就進入完全不同的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是龍宮島特有的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎和劍司一如既往的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還賭劍司贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士賭哪邊贏?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提劍司是13連敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去可是很要好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎和總士 他們倆小時候常在一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在一起玩是有原因的吧 相互之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事要低頭懇求身為副會長的你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫我養著它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋！帶它一起走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我有事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 僚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 藏前 接下來的事拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長竟然先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道明天有休學典禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不想說是去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天他能撐著來就已經很辛苦了 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 那傢伙是個懶蟲也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們加油幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的 只是有些貧血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你還挺熱心腸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為看你表情很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎沒跟其他人一起回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別老等著劍司那樣的人衝到面前來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要主動和別人搞好關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說你幫了我 說這話好像不大厚道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧有你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去遠見醫生那邊喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我這就走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間也來作檢查?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚睡覺之前還好好的 今天卻不能上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是遺傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長得的病跟媽媽一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然和媽媽沒有血緣關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.35,0:07:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很羨慕羽佐間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有位真心體貼你的好母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,症狀穩定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,減少止疼藥的劑量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 無法再復原了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.18,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,症狀也有可能完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說那個選拔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚 情況一定不會悲觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 聽說可以自願參加 鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最害怕一事無成就結束了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母親去世已經兩年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨立生活有困難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島這麼小 總有人幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說 我也不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽佐間 不回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢馬上就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 有個好朋友真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的好朋友一半以上都「畢業」了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持上學 還當學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在我休假時 大家擅自決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自決定?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 一上學就突然多了個頭銜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然這樣 不覺得討厭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像硬塞給你似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家沒有忘記我 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們為我準備了容身之處 我應該報恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算去學校 恐怕也沒有容身之處了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍惜陪在你身邊的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校長 真壁叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我馬上去沏茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 只是來打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們走了 生駒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心養病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 今天上午又舉行「畢業」典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放暑假之前 舉行好幾次「畢業」典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這裡是個荒僻的小島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸小時候的畢業典禮也是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我「畢業」後會去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門重複發出反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預計700小時之內將得到明確應答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不能迎擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的核正在形成人格 若此時和敵人接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整座島都被奪取的可能性太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是只能將防禦系統降低到極限嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們直接跟生駒談了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重點將全部{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnSimHei}相關兵器嚴密封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為將被敵人奪取後的打擊降到最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能主動封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 僅此實在不能算是萬全之策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對此生駒所提出迴避危機的計劃 即是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnSimHei}計劃?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若要實施 {\fnArial}TSX{\fnSimHei}的投入是大前提
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 難道要讓孩子們參與嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:12:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要掌控這個島的人們共同決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（暑假）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一定要打贏你 別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天要和朋友出去一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友約我去海邊玩 很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒讓我想起這島雖小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候卻也不愁找不到地方玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你約我來的 自己卻不下去游嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你的泳姿 就失去信心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你去看過遠見醫生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 只是有些不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微能明白這樣的人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直和爸爸生活在一起 習慣照顧人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體也曬暖了 去游一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒想過讓別人照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果傷了你的心 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很開心 許久未曾這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至能稍微拋開爸爸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Al…vis…{\fnSimHei}必須…得去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去{\fnArial}Alvis…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士同學 令尊常去看我父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 說是在公事上聽取一些建議
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnSimHei}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Plan…L
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnSimHei}計劃?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner…Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnSimHei}是為了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在嗎 你在那裡嗎 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,識別限制編碼確認為第三級
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道這些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}TSX
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}TS…X
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝賀你「畢業」 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.00,0:19:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的聲音一直在我腦海裡迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催眠學習({\fnArial}Memorizing{\fnSimHei})的知識\N是作為聲音來被認知的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到的是媽媽的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催眠學習?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小開始就被無意識灌輸的各種知識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現今的世界形勢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在於島內部的{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及與敵人戰鬥的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnSimHei}的人就算「畢業」了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦知道 就無法回到平常的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.51,0:19:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要選擇和大人們一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚為什麼沒有離開島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父親所設立的拯救島的L計劃啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對父親的事情一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親一定想讓我參加這個計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才會念著{\fnArial}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 你還什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就一直都明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒跟你出去 爸爸就不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要選擇和父親相同的道路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您成全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的指令書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何也要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下終於可以報答給我容身之處的人們了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 選拔成員聚齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠自主催眠學習
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.89,0:22:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,協成率形成度高的最適格者們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:22:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是今天起負責各位訓練的日野惠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想退出作戰的人可隨時向我提出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.97,0:23:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼開始說明{\fnArial}L{\fnSimHei}計劃的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnSimHei}的全貌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在敵人正逐漸察覺此島的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.69,0:23:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnSimHei}計劃正是為了避免之
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.96,0:23:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnSimHei}即指{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnSimHei}的左翼 {\fnArial}L{\fnSimHei}區域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將其從島上分離開 成為{\fnArial}L Boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnSimHei}能夠在超越敵人探知能力的深海中前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到島的防禦圈外上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引敵人 按既定航線繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為期兩個月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要讓其誤以為{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnSimHei}就是龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須持續迎擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這艘{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnSimHei}是自動駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連自己身在何處也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這將是極其苛刻的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想退出的人請提出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼立即開始訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.49,0:24:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnSimHei}的第一大特徵 即無需操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.52,0:24:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要遵從催眠學習獲得的知識 和{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnSimHei}一體化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.13,0:24:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受精神的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是訓練用的虛擬現實
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.53,0:24:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.24,0:24:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.80,0:24:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…{\fnArial}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.59,0:24:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.28,0:24:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能跑 這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.12,0:24:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸毫無困難
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.74,0:24:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 這不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.58,0:24:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.08,0:24:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二大特徵 即各機內置系統間的交叉({\fnArial}Crossing{\fnSimHei})
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.54,0:24:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共享思考 防止被敵人讀取
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.87,0:25:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要接受同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.63,0:25:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.58,0:25:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.19,0:25:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.08,0:25:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 請換其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.97,0:25:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了取得平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.91,0:25:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是他 你馬上就能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.05,0:25:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.04,0:25:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.08,0:25:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未 你害怕了?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.56,0:25:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是僚的感覺?你在享受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.36,0:25:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘上這個 我也能游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.75,0:25:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制時間到 請離開駕駛艙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.02,0:25:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnSimHei}的第三大特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.17,0:25:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即駕駛員會被同化現象所侵擾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.35,0:25:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐次數越多 肉體越容易發生異常
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.05,0:25:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最壞情況下可能危及生命
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.81,0:25:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退出吧 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.47,0:26:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹不了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.46,0:26:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了爸爸一定要讓計劃成功
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.95,0:26:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是一開始就不想活著回去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.23,0:26:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如退出算了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.51,0:26:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選拔成員共8人 無人退出
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.36,0:26:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnSimHei}共4架 每架由兩人交替駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.34,0:26:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次戰鬥時間15分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.44,0:26:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人交替 各戰鬥450秒
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.97,0:26:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷重複的戰鬥訓練 以及敵人的確認
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.83,0:26:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矽狀生命體－{\fnArial}Festum {\fnSimHei}即敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.68,0:26:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有統一的思考 能適應任何環境
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.03,0:26:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但未曾在海中發現過
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.84,0:26:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據推測是其若與海中結晶物同化
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.85,0:26:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會成為不規則塊狀物
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.01,0:26:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是「畢業」的準備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.91,0:26:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而對我來說 還有一項重要的準備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.10,0:27:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 普庫 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.49,0:27:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我給的 它從不吃任何食物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.05,0:27:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定察覺到會被丟下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.24,0:27:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能帶狗一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.28,0:27:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為飼主 要負起責任
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.46,0:27:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條狗是從前媽媽帶回來 讓我當成朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.71,0:27:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法去上學時
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.53,0:27:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有它在身邊 我就不會感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.70,0:27:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.00,0:27:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明知有毒還去吃的對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.50,0:27:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.20,0:27:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝婆婆    我下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.20,0:28:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.44,0:28:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖等著學長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.67,0:28:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為獎勵 學長們的慰問品分你一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.53,0:28:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在Nothung model正在啟動測試中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.53,0:28:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中的新型{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnSimHei}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.62,0:28:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.60,0:28:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個月後計劃完畢之前 應該趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.83,0:28:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們沒事 就能來迎接我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.35,0:28:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.12,0:28:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長 它好像肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.97,0:28:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.69,0:28:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這是隨身物品 可能有些沉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.21,0:28:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.01,0:28:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.96,0:28:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我會把它當成學長好好珍視
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.83,0:28:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.84,0:28:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是做好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.93,0:28:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.11,0:28:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣 完成最後一項準備時
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.53,0:28:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為何想起了祐未的話
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.61,0:29:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始就覺得回不去的人 應該退出
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.12,0:29:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.37,0:29:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 多半祐未是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.96,0:29:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偽裝鏡面 維持{\fnArial}ROM{\fnSimHei}模式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.03,0:29:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接續區域 全部隔離壁以緊急模式封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.97,0:29:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全隔離壁封鎖確認
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.69,0:29:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開啟注水閥
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.35,0:29:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接續區域 確認注水
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.81,0:29:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnSimHei}艦橋呼叫{\fnArial}CDC
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.05,0:29:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,程序鏈接無異常
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.86,0:29:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注水完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.99,0:29:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat {\fnSimHei}出發準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.95,0:29:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnSimHei}區域分離準備 全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.69,0:29:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分離
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.08,0:29:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L Boat{\fnSimHei}控制程序開始運行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.90,0:29:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駛向波盾圈外
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.90,0:29:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個月後再會
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.62,0:29:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝他們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.95,0:29:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二步驟啟動 作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.08,0:29:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.71,0:30:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距離計劃結束的時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.85,0:30:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9月2號 {\fnArial}L{\fnSimHei}計劃啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.13,0:30:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}L{\fnSimHei}即{\fnArial}Left {\fnSimHei}左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.52,0:30:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也含有離去的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.54,0:30:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如這個詞所說 我們離開了島
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.29,0:30:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發後第3天 我們的小島上浮了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.94,0:30:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天起 這裡就是龍宮島了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.49,0:30:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人實體化 是{\fnArial}Sphinx {\fnSimHei}型
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.72,0:30:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以普通武器牽制 {\fnArial}Fafner {\fnSimHei}準備出擊
