Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.40,0:30:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Brunhild{\fnSimHei}系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.79,0:30:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnSimHei}搭乘輸入優先
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.84,0:30:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}數據線確認
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.85,0:30:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}速度控制
