Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.01,0:30:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}各機正常
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.34,0:30:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}封鎖解除
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.86,0:30:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Niebelungen{\fnSimHei}系統開啟確認
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.62,0:30:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}{\fnArial}Siegfried{\fnSimHei}系統接續完成
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.96,0:30:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18}接續桿連接
