Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.92,0:44:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.87,0:44:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.74,0:44:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.61,0:44:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防禦圈內有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.52,0:44:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是潛水艇和{\fnArial}Titan-model
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.37,0:44:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備出擊 總士
