Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.20,0:44:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著我  一定把你帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.20,0:44:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中間正面出現{\fnArial}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.09,0:44:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短魚雷及導彈戰準備
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.16,0:44:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,252度也出現敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.61,0:44:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.60,0:45:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnSimHei}呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.31,0:45:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後方約20公里處
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.47,0:45:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.46,0:45:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們幾時能下水了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.50,0:45:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛水艇消失
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.90,0:45:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.69,0:45:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島應該在這個方向 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.20,0:45:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.18,0:45:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.29,0:45:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已經知道龍宮島在這前面了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.19,0:45:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.85,0:45:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能百分之百確定 就不能這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.84,0:45:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易活到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.21,0:45:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回去 回島上去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.59,0:45:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況已經變了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.05,0:45:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不能讓大家的戰鬥失去意義
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.74,0:45:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 在有人來迎接我們之前
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.49,0:45:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學長  拜託你...不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.89,0:45:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Titan-model{\fnSimHei}開始移動
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.26,0:45:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠離島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.31,0:46:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士 停住{\fnArial}Mark Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.67,0:46:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能發生了最壞的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.28,0:46:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.77,0:46:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓整座島置身險境 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.67,0:46:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Mark Zwei {\fnSimHei}停止前進
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.81,0:46:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 不去接學長他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.44,0:46:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地待機 {\fnArial}Mark Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.06,0:46:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況變了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.27,0:46:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 不是要去接學長他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.24,0:46:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.76,0:46:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原地待機！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.28,0:46:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我絕不認同
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.73,0:46:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎖定{\fnArial}Mark Zwei{\fnSimHei}的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.53,0:46:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你讓我去 皆城 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.43,0:46:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城 聽得見吧 為什麼不說話
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.00,0:46:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 皆城 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.14,0:46:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.53,0:46:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}CDC {\fnSimHei}那邊是有著實戰經驗的機體和駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.90,0:46:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能回收那些數據
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.75,0:47:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的戰力將大幅提升
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.42,0:47:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也更能抵抗敵人的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.31,0:47:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.34,0:47:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獲得與敵人戰鬥力量的絕好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.34,0:47:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您打算眼睜睜地錯過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.43,0:47:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnSimHei}是做什麼用的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.65,0:47:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.89,0:47:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不能讓{\fnArial}Fafner{\fnSimHei}離開防禦圈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.78,0:47:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.58,0:47:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Mark Zwei {\fnSimHei}重整機體
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.24,0:47:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後全力追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.20,0:47:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.85,0:47:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,計測目標周邊所有振動
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.18,0:47:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.81,0:47:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就能得到答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.36,0:47:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潮流的數據收集到了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.57,0:47:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在這裡運氣好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.61,0:47:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少殘骸能回到島上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.48,0:47:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.84,0:47:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.36,0:48:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 制止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.33,0:48:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.48,0:48:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.27,0:48:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.71,0:48:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我一直喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.06,0:48:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能 從很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.01,0:48:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道是不是喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.96,0:48:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時 已經超越了那種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.23,0:48:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.29,0:48:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.40,0:48:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島上的人們會知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.96,0:48:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.27,0:48:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸會稱讚我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.42,0:49:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪?下在海底?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.88,0:49:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海雪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.88,0:49:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs20}注:海底浮游生物組成的絮狀物，看起來像雪
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.79,0:49:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在稱讚我們呢 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.85,0:49:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僚
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.52,0:49:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在陪在我身邊的是你 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.55,0:49:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.16,0:49:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.01,0:49:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.45,0:49:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好像還有更多更深的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.58,0:49:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你陪在身邊 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.52,0:50:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.98,0:50:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.68,0:50:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了嗎 祐未
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.21,0:50:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.91,0:50:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈禱有人能聽到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.54,0:50:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你們以前從未到過海中
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.68,0:50:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由於無法代謝而結晶化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.66,0:51:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代謝…就是使身體重生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.40,0:51:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也掌握了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.31,0:51:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 才擁有了生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.35,0:51:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnArial}Fenrir{\fnSimHei}釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.52,0:51:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認信源地
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.24,0:51:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判斷為海底有人啟動了{\fnArial}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.09,0:51:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.89,0:51:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心機體被敵人同化
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.74,0:51:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說明海底也存在{\fnArial}Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.77,0:51:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是給我們的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.99,0:51:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mark Zwei 返航
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.59,0:51:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡已經 沒有任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.00,0:52:05.76,pic8,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,276)\fad(2000,2000)\fscx150}四\N個\N月\N後
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.00,0:52:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是第一波盾的潮流感應器探查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.24,0:52:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著珍貴的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.99,0:52:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.08,0:52:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 分析了潮流後才啟動的{\fnArial}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.58,0:52:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是保持鎮靜直到最後的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.30,0:52:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰駕駛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.64,0:52:28.17,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,どれくらい時間があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.64,0:52:28.17,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,要經過多少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.51,0:52:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據調查 似乎只留下了音頻記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.95,0:52:32.83,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心は繫がるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.95,0:52:32.83,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,心才能相映
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.83,0:52:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 普庫 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.07,0:52:39.61,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,どこか寂しげな笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.07,0:52:39.61,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,些許寂寞的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.37,0:52:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.97,0:52:44.07,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,癒せたらいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.97,0:52:44.07,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,多想將其治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.69,0:52:52.10,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,近すぎて氣づけなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.69,0:52:52.10,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,太過靠近而未曾察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.91,0:52:57.26,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,一番大事な人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.91,0:52:57.26,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.42,0:52:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是我們的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.87,0:53:03.64,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,傍に居てくれるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.87,0:53:03.64,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,只是陪在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.45,0:53:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈禱有人能聽到這些
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.95,0:53:09.31,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,幸せを感じられる
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.95,0:53:09.31,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.51,0:53:12.39,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しみの夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.51,0:53:12.39,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,悲傷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.46,0:53:15.39,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,喜びの朝も
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.46,0:53:15.39,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,喜悅的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.46,0:53:21.42,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしを見守ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.46,0:53:21.42,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,都將我守候
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.93,0:53:27.58,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,ただ一言「ありがとう」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.93,0:53:27.58,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,連一句感謝的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.92,0:53:32.91,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,伝えられないままで
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.92,0:53:32.91,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,也未能傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.40,0:53:36.31,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,素直になるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.40,0:53:36.31,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,要變得率直
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.34,0:53:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普庫
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.44,0:53:39.27,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,少し怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.44,0:53:39.27,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,還有些膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.25,0:53:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 待在這裡的是將陵學長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.48,0:53:45.19,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,今あなたの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.48,0:53:45.19,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,如今在你懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.89,0:53:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定是陪伴祐未學姐直到最後的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.99,0:53:51.89,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心がほどけてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.99,0:53:51.89,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,心漸漸釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.13,0:54:01.09,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,溫かい安らぎに抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.13,0:54:01.09,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,被溫暖平靜擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.89,0:54:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起 一定是去了將陵學長身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.64,0:54:16.10,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,靜けさにふと窗の外
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.64,0:54:16.10,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,窗外靜靜地
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.52,0:54:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先回去了 想把它送回龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.96,0:54:20.87,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,雪が舞い降りている
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.96,0:54:20.87,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,飄起了雪
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.32,0:54:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所羅門的反應顯示著徵兆
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.92,0:54:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預計很快將輪到{\fnArial}Alvis{\fnSimHei}迎擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.96,0:54:27.25,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,真白に染まる世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.96,0:54:27.25,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,在純白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.98,0:54:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平僅僅維持了半年
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.01,0:54:33.23,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたの音に寄り添う
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.01,0:54:33.23,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,依偎著你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.45,0:54:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將陵學長他們的戰鬥 只有這點意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.51,0:54:36.31,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,素直になるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.51,0:54:36.31,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,要變得率直
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.92,0:54:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直享受著別人贏來並讓給的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.45,0:54:39.38,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,少し怖かった
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.45,0:54:39.38,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,還有些膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.55,0:54:44.90,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたの腕の中
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.55,0:54:44.90,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,如今在你懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.82,0:54:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便那和平只有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.99,0:54:51.86,ed,NTP,0,0,0,,心がほどけてゆく
